{"id":409,"date":"2014-10-20T12:19:17","date_gmt":"2014-10-20T12:19:17","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/icpbees.org\/?p=409"},"modified":"2017-05-23T12:36:48","modified_gmt":"2017-05-23T16:36:48","slug":"california-almond-industry-moves-to-protect-vital-bee-colonies","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/icpbees.org\/california-almond-industry-moves-to-protect-vital-bee-colonies\/","title":{"rendered":"California Almond Industry Moves to Protect Vital Bee Colonies"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"fcbkbttn_buttons_block\" id=\"fcbkbttn_left\"><\/div><p>The importance of honeybees to California\u2019s almond crop is written across the state\u2019s landscape every February \u2013 when an armada of trucks filled with beehives enters the state.<\/p>\n<div>\n<section class=\"container main-content \">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-offset-1 col-lg-10&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;\ncol-xs-12\"><\/p>\n<div id=\"tabs-c4c6f9be\" class=\"story-tabs\">\n<div class=\"tab-content \">\n<div id=\"tabs-c4c6f9be-tabPane-1\" class=\"tab-pane active\">\n<div class=\"row \">\n<div id=\"story-content\" class=\"col-sm-7 border-right\">\n<div id=\"story-target\">\n<div id=\"content-body-713359-2929956\">\n<p>Without the bees to pollinate the trees, there would be no almond crop.<\/p>\n<p>The importance of honeybees is now written across a first-ever set of public\u00a0guidelines for almond growers and beekeepers, released Thursday by the California Almond Board. The guidelines are meant to safeguard bees, whose winter numbers have plunged.<\/p>\n<div><a title=\"Read more\" href=\"http:\/\/www.sacbee.com\/news\/business\/article2929956.html\" target=\"_blank\">Read more<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The importance of honeybees to California\u2019s almond crop